{"tid":527428,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方拘32歲印傭涉非法墮胎及棄置嬰屍","createTime":"2018-01-12T15:38:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T16:39:16.000Z","uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"71f2fe125c98d5b0eb73e9db94382db6b710f5ff","tid":527428,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T15:38:55.000Z","msg":"警方拘捕一名三十二歲印傭，涉嫌非法墮胎，將嬰兒屍體棄置在牛頭角彩霞邨彩星樓的垃圾房，她目前仍被扣查。<br />\n<br />\n這名印傭凌晨前往聯合醫院求醫，醫護人員檢查後，懷疑她曾分娩，警方接報到場調查，在彩星樓的垃圾房發現一個已死亡的胎兒，懷疑印傭曾服用藥物墮胎，再將胎兒丟棄在一個垃圾箱。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=986885&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D986885%26csid%3D261_341&d=msISmKu3qs%2Bss7JSZTKL0wEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=240ab37c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=986885&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"6bd8940ffecea149c7de3a5adc346966b9379503","tid":527428,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T15:41:48.000Z","msg":"又係垃圾印狗<br />\n除咗佔領道路天橋外又一傑作"},{"pid":"aee995cb9ea5f67a6ec575c7ce81da45cde125e9","tid":527428,"uid":44073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T15:43:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0dbadef78c05b97c43b86a769271eaaa5544a81a","tid":527428,"uid":67500,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T15:43:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/12/234344_ff070e5564123da6aeccab9c4d093d41.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F12%2F234344_ff070e5564123da6aeccab9c4d093d41.png&h=147b012d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港印印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa36616e75c8ab52f6666c624469e09523eb1846","tid":527428,"uid":73613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T15:44:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"184e7a92f3a03134b0bb408d3f37d63804e163d3","tid":527428,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aee995cb9ea5f67a6ec575c7ce81da45cde125e9","tid":527428,"uid":44073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6bd8940ffecea149c7de3a5adc346966b9379503","tid":527428,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T15:41:48.000Z","msg":"又係垃圾印狗<br />\n除咗佔領道路天橋外又一傑作"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T15:43:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T15:46:48.000Z","msg":"我知<br />\n但咪又係一鬼樣"},{"pid":"d2971cd21b60c0da59653c99f378bb49edc9bf78","tid":527428,"uid":22869,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T15:47:37.000Z","msg":"No...problem..."},{"pid":"6a8100fc55c134d2fa62299ddde7bf6c3c532fda","tid":527428,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T15:48:13.000Z","msg":"【19:25】消息稱，警方撿獲的是女嬰屍體<br />\n【17:16】警方調查顯示，涉事女傭自2015年起在事發單位打工，有人報稱不知自己懷孕，因沒有來經多個月，遂到牛頭角一街市購買通經藥並服下，結果誕下嬰兒。嬰兒誕下時仍有心跳，女傭涉嫌殺嬰<br />\n【16:10】新增內容<br />\n<br />\n牛頭角彩霞邨彩星樓一名32歲印尼女傭，深夜時份到聯合醫院求診，醫護人員經檢驗，發現她體內有殘餘胎盤，相信她曾經分娩，遂於凌晨1時報警。警方到女子所報的彩星樓住址，未有發現嬰兒，但在屋內撿獲懷疑用作墮胎的藥物，隨即將搜索範圍擴大，終於大廈地下垃圾房內撿獲一具嬰屍，初步估計31周大，懷疑印尼女服藥墮胎後，再將嬰兒棄於垃圾房，於是把她拘捕帶署扣查。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，嬰屍被人棄置在彩星樓5樓的垃圾房，其後沿垃圾槽跌落地下垃圾房。警方調查顯示，涉事女傭自2015年起在事發單位打工，有人報稱不知自己懷孕，因沒有來經多個月，遂到牛頭角一街市購買通經藥並服下。消息稱，女事主曾服用藥一日，結果誕下嬰兒。嬰兒誕下時仍有呼吸心跳，女傭涉嫌殺嬰。<br />\n<br />\n在港合法墮胎必須經醫生確認後，在醫院或家計會進行，否則都屬違法。一般人以為藥物墮胎是無痛方法，甚至與事後丸混淆，但其實服藥後會子宮持續出血二至三星期才能排出胚胎，而且因為子宮收縮痛楚感會持續一段時間。懷孕九周或以下的婦女才適合使用藥物墮胎，若有宮外孕、藥物過敏、吸煙量大等的女性，則皆不適用藥物流產。<br />\n<br />\n根據法例212章《侵害人身罪條例》，如證明母親已懷孕28個星期或以上，須推定該母親當時懷有可活產的胎兒。而任何人意圖毀滅可活產的胎兒的生命，導致胎兒在獨立於母體而存在之前死亡，即屬犯殺胎罪，可處以刑罰，猶如他已犯誤殺罪一樣，一旦罪成，最高可判終身監禁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180112/57697450\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180112%2F57697450&d=msISmKu3qs%2Bss7JSZTKL0wEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=5232abb0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180112%2F57697450&h=a246e949\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180112/57697450</a>"},{"pid":"ccb90aedc2a969f0c2d8517d529d34d739500f71","tid":527428,"uid":33864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T15:52:23.000Z","msg":"如果個master有份就害個工人成世"},{"pid":"b9d82e132522238c68d70474581c2df90975fcbe","tid":527428,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T15:57:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46302ee483b72d7f2fe3f45f051c93e86f3f46f9","tid":527428,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T16:38:52.000Z","msg":"香港女權團體應該要幫下個印印啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女體覺煮啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> pro choice 啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88cb4461fb16a8b110040d79e15dbfedfe97ff02","tid":527428,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T16:39:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港女權團體應該要幫下個印印啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女體自煮啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> pro choice 啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"}]}